description:
*Please notice: This package is not supported by Sitecore A/S*

Requires Sitecore 7.1.

Contains more than 70 new SPEAK renderings that wrap 85% of Twitter Bootstrap 2.3.2.

Additional renderings include:
- FuelUX Spinner
- InlineStyle
- AjaxDataSource
- StaticJsonDataSource
- Debugger
- KnockoutModelPresenter

Additional rule actions include:
-  ServerCall

After installing navigate to /sitecore/client/Speak-Stuff/Content/Bootstrap/Scaffolding
